Class DirectedWeightedPseudograph<V,E>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, DirectedGraph<V,E>, Graph<V,E>, WeightedGraph<V,E>

    public class DirectedWeightedPseudograph<V,E>
extends DirectedPseudograph<V,E>
implements WeightedGraph<V,E>
    A directed weighted pseudograph. A directed weighted pseudograph is a non-simple directed graph in which both graph loops and multiple edges are permitted, and edges have weights.
